<br>
ANY guild that requires you to have a VT key is unreasonable.  If they are farming VT 24-7 and don't really care about killing in Ssra, then they are probably not recruiting anyways and that requirement of having a VT key is just some nice way of saying: &quot;We are currently not recruiting, but are in the stage of farming in VT.&quot;  Requiring a VP key is not so unreasonable.  It's not so bad questing for it, just a big timesink.  And there are rumors that it is being revamped soon.  Requiring an ST key is just ridiculous, because guilds don't raid there in force anymore, and the only reason to go is to get prismatic weapons.  Any guild that wants you to have an ST key is like saying, &quot;We want to help you farm for prismatic weapons!&quot; and that is probably a blatant lie. <p><img src="http://www.geocities.com/dakkan2001/xsigtest1.gif">
