I dunno if its a Morell Thule only thing, but on our server, there are many guild alliances.  There is even a guild alliance that consists of 3 or 4 guilds or something (GoB).  Sometimes, if u can pull the 55+s from multiple guilds, you realize you can raid some pretty big things.<br>
